## Result

GREEN for the bridge-loop activation slice:

- fresh trigger rows were claimed within about 1 second;
- visible target-agent messages were persisted for easy, medium, hard, and
  extra-hard diagnostic tasks;
- all target triggers completed within about 17 seconds;
- terminal reverse triggers were closed without a response loop.

Remaining caveat: this proves the workspace bridge loop, not a native Pentagon
app trigger poller repair.
